{"tid":350563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIVE][多圖] 東京+大阪 十日九夜之旅","createTime":"2017-08-07T10:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T11:20:17.000Z","uid":63968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47d2f0c2bf81aed95e3eceebd15fad664dd7cd51","tid":350563,"uid":63968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"之前出左咁多關於大陸既旅遊post<br />\n<br />\n今次專登出番個其他地方既旅遊post<br />\n<br />\n某程度上係我向中學同學今次係我補鑊既trip<br />\n<br />\n話說之前中學畢業放左中學同學飛機冇同佢地去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後比佢地屌到上天花板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後到依加大家大學畢業先搵到機會再去旅行<br />\n<br />\n決定去旅行去到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  黎個東京+大阪 十日九夜畢業之旅<br />\n<br />\n以下是plan左既行程 不過我估實有變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTokyo<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 (7/8):<br />\n新宿check in 酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 (8/8):<br />\n築地<br />\n皇宮(千代)<br />\n雷門<br />\n東宮寓所(Maybe)<br />\n台場(Maybe)<br />\n博物館<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 (9/8):<br />\n手信 + Shopping<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 (10/8):<br />\n自由活動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOsaka<br />\n<br />\n11th - Travel to Osaka from Tokyo<br />\n<br />\n12th - 京都(清水寺/金閣寺/比叡山/伏見稻荷大社)<br />\n<br />\n13th - 奈良 &rarr; 心齋橋/道頓堀/黑門市場<br />\n<br />\n14th - 神戶 &rarr;  梅田<br />\n<br />\n15th - USJ (自由活動)<br />\n<br />\n16th - 手信 + 自由活動 --&gt; 番香港"},{"pid":"e0143cb9fc36c94214ff3614ae91dca9498eb037","tid":350563,"uid":63968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"今日坐早機 9點鬆d機<br />\n<br />\n坐cx <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/184750_ddfec9c6c78434edc6156f966a868daf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F184750_ddfec9c6c78434edc6156f966a868daf.jpg&h=b514977a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係坐走廊位 所以d leg space 都幾多下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/184753_10835e023764eddcd736325a10ed21b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F184753_10835e023764eddcd736325a10ed21b4.jpg&h=ebd99671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機餐睇落都唔錯 係差在杯哈根大師 (ka飛福岡係有既）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/184959_b9bd9dd8203dfe7a1bccb432a2eb5032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F184959_b9bd9dd8203dfe7a1bccb432a2eb5032.jpg&h=62d1719b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"814c2119cbc1a9e3a2752d0052448d3df51d43f2","tid":350563,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />沒人"},{"pid":"7cc70a9c5d0ead39261ab225cbe0bb23a9571805","tid":350563,"uid":18058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:20:17.000Z","msg":"LM"}]}